  "pageTitle": "骨料回收参考案例",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page case-study-detail-page case-study-detail-page-industrial\"> <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"case-detail-title\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">C&amp;D 废弃物案例</p> <h1 id=\"case-detail-title\">骨料回收参考案例</h1> <p class=\"hero-copy\">一体化骨料回收处理线参考，生产回收骨料和分离可回收材料。</p></section> <section class=\"section case-detail-section case-detail-timeline-section\" id=\"construction-waste-utilization\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-waste-utilization-timeline-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">系统流程</p> <h2 id=\"construction-waste-utilization-timeline-title\">案例范围连接场地条件、工艺范围与回收产出</h2> <p>案例按项目评估流程排序：背景、合作单位、限制、解决方案以及前后对比。</p></div> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline\" aria-label=\"案例流程时间线\"> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>01</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">项目背景</p> <h3>混合现场物料压力</h3> <p>该项目将混合建筑与装饰废弃物转化为可再利用产出，减少直接填埋压力。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>物料类别</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 类物料流</strong><span>建筑与装饰废弃物</span></dd></div> <div><dt>输出方向</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">3 类产出</strong><span>骨料 / 金属 / 轻质材料</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>02</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">合作单位</p> <h3>区域资源化运营</h3> <p>合作单位正在扩大骨料回收，需要一条可参考的处理线，供项目团队按废弃物类型、场地条件和设备范围进行比较。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>操作人员类型</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 地区团队</strong><span>废弃物资源化企业</span></dd></div> <div><dt>评审重点</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 项检查</strong><span>材料 / 场地 / 范围 / 视频</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>03</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">实际限制</p> <h3>户外堆场布局限制</h3> <p>布局必须考虑装载机供料、设备基础区域、骨料堆场、金属收集和轻质物料分离处理。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>场地面积</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">5 个区域</strong><span>稳定给料至暂存</span></dd></div> <div><dt>场地限制</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 场地</strong><span>户外物流占地</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>04</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">解决方案</p> <h3>集成分离配置</h3> <p>设备范围结合了送料、破碎、骨料筛分、磁性分离、气流分离、输送、粉尘控制接口和输出收集。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>处理能力参考</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">70 t/h</strong><span>· Lion One 处理线</span></dd></div> <div><dt>核心流程</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 工序</strong><span>破碎 / 筛分 / 磁选 / 气流</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>05</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">前后对比</p> <h3>回收产出路径记录</h3> <div class=\"case-detail-comparison\"> <div><span>之前</span><strong>场地物料混杂，流向不清晰</strong><p>建筑和装饰废弃物需要多次处理步骤，才能看到可回收的部分。</p></div> <div><span>之后</span><strong>从稳定给料到库存的综合流程</strong><p>视频内容涵盖送料、破碎、骨料筛分、磁性分离、气流分离以及最终输出堆。</p></div></div> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>视频范围</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">6 个步骤</strong><span>给料至输出</span></dd></div></dl></div></article></div></section> <section class=\"section case-detail-action-section industrial-rfq-section ai-layout-reference\" aria-label=\"案例操作\"> <div class=\"rfq-action-strip case-detail-action-strip\"> <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求参考包</a> <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">返回参考案例</a></div></section></main>"
}
